=== METEORITE_CORE ===
# id: 5
# title: The Meteorite Core
# chinese_title: 陨核
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A meteorite has punctured the outer hull and lodged itself in the corridor. Its core glows with residual heat, and your scanner detects rare minerals within. The impact has cracked open the rock, revealing veins of iridescent ore.

* [Mine the rare minerals]
  ~ gain_radical("石")
  "石" (shí) — stone, rock
* [Collect ore samples for trade]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "矿" (kuàng) — ore, mineral
* [Study the meteorite's trajectory data]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "天" (tiān) — sky, heaven
